item.title: METAL GEAR SOLID Δ: SNAKE EATER Cast Interview
item.description:
Join us as we delve into the much-anticipated revival of "Metal Gear Solid Δ: Snake Eater." In this episode, we explore the game's cinematic brilliance and its impact on new generations. Hear from the cast as they share insights on re-recording iconic lines and working with the legendary team. Whether you're a long-time fan or new to the series, this episode offers a captivating look at what makes "Snake Eater" a timeless masterpiece.
